# Set the default behavior, in case people don't have core.autocrlf set.
# https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/getting-started-with-git/configuring-git-to-handle-line-endings
# this was build in windows, so using .devcontainers with ubuntu/debian will struggle with windows line endings
# and mark all files as changed, even if git will not tell you what has changed directly.
* text=auto